data.description: Welcome to this beautiful single story home with captivating upgrades and features! This spotless home comes with all appliances, a new zero turn mower, and a luxurious 20 by 30 shop. Four spacious bedrooms and a large flex room which can be transformed into a huge 5th bedroom or living area. That's not all, the home is surrounded by a fully landscaped yard including an in-ground full-coverage sprinkler system, french drains, high-end decorative rocks, and an exquisite outdoor fire pit area. Added peace of mind with storm doors, a 12 person storm shelter, ring doorbell, and a hard-wired home surveillance system. The home is energy efficient with dual-pane windows, private well water, a whole home water purification system, and an aerobic septic system. Added features include: tile throughout the living area and hallways, granite countertops, custom cabinets, and fiber internet. Conveniently 5 minutes from the Historic City of Guthrie and Highway 35. Come sit back and enjoy the peace and tranquility of the country's fresh air on the covered front and back patios. Lots of wildlife to see. The backyard opens to a impeccable oasis. Schedule your tour today and make an offer!
